channel.title: Why does it tell me my 5555 port is in use already?
channel.description:
A while back, I put the server I downloaded online(Pimpscape) & now everytime I try to put it online, it tells me that port 5555 is already in use. When I check the "Server Status" page, my server's also online but it won't let me join it... I just want to know 1 of 2 things:
1. How do I get my server off of the server status page(if you even can) 2. How come it's saying port 5555's in use already?
Would appreciate an answer quick. Thanks!
